commentary: Rabada to Mohammad Hafeez, OUT oh, what a catch! Phehlukwayo, take a bow! This is a screamer, I tell you. Hafeez drills this fuller one uppishly, backs himself to clear mid-off, and you can't fault him for thinking so. After all, you don't see catches such as those everyday. Phehlukwayo moves to his left from mid-off, runs a few steps and takes flight, back arched towards his left, hands outstretched and taking it clean as he comes tumbling down
shortText: Rabada to Mohammad Hafeez, OUT
text: oh, what a catch! Phehlukwayo, take a bow! This is a screamer, I tell you. Hafeez drills this fuller one uppishly, backs himself to clear mid-off, and you can't fault him for thinking so. After all, you don't see catches such as those everyday. Phehlukwayo moves to his left from mid-off, runs a few steps and takes flight, back arched towards his left, hands outstretched and taking it clean as he comes tumbling down
